<https://example.com/id/OntarioChestDiseaseService> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Ontario. Chest Disease Service" .
<https://example.com/id/OntarioChestDiseaseService> <https://www.ica.org/standards/RiC/ontology#generalDescription> "Function Note: The Chest Disease Service was established to eradicate tuberculosis and to deal with other diseases of the chest and lungs." .
